Package project3

Class Species

Object
Species
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Species>
public class Species extends Object implements Comparable<Species>
This class represents a single species, encapsulating its common name, scientific name, taxonomic information, conservation status in New York, and presence in counties. It implements the Comparable interface.
